    "description": "<p>Flowtek Engineering Pte Ltd is Singapore based organisation and in the field of provision of engineering services for semi-conductor, pharmaceutical and related industries, including maintenance, pipes and equipment / tools hook-up, servicing, repair and fabrication of process-flow piping.</p>\n\n<p>Our Special strengths include skilled knowledge of process planning, layout and detailed Engineering Drafting inclusive of skid and piping space management. We are also highly experienced in planning, project execution and commissioning of large-scale plants and equipment. And highly proficient in the execution of DI & Waste Water Treatment Plant and Chemical Dispense System piping installation.</p>\n\n<p>FLowtek Engineering Pte Ltd has been awarded the BCEA Top 10 Engineering Companies (2013 Building  Construction Excellence Award)</p>\n",
